{
  "stem": "21812.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm wondering at this point-- and I haven't thought about that, but because-- it must have been very close to High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think we were already evacuated into Colne, Lancashire, and there wouldn't have been any chance of-- because it was too small a town.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think there were Jewish-- I wasn't aware of any Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we stayed there for about four or five months, till-- again, I don't remember how I got back to Bradford-- till the government decided that there would be no danger of imminent-- of bombings at that point.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there were sporadic bombings going on, but no mass destruction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the children went back to their original homes at that point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I went back to Bradford, and I-- back to the same couple.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I apprenticed to that-- I was apprenticed to that electrician.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did a little bit of work, very little, because they had very little-- what happened, the private-- the-- the private work stopped during the war and the government work hadn't started yet, so they were sort of in between, and I didn't-- I worked in the office a little bit, I did this, but very-- very little.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got a couple of dollars, a couple of pounds or whatever, not pounds, but whatever money, I did get a little money, earned a little bit of money, so I had some money.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that time, I was in Bradford till April, 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- my affidavit was coming through at that point, and I had to go to London by myself in the blackout.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "England was totally blacked out at that point, totally.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
